descriptionNullable:
### Context

This dataset collected from [airbnb](http://insideairbnb.com/get-the-data.html). It is collected to see how airbnb is used in Turkey Istanbul.


### Content

There are 16 columns which shows the latitude, longitude etc. It also shows the price. So, a regression problem such as finding the price of an house can be applied to this dataset. To see an example you can check  [my notebook](https://www.kaggle.com/ocakhsn/airbnb-price-prediction-multiple-datasets) from airbnb newyork dataset
